text:
Hey everyone! I'm currently working with the v3 *List associations of a contact by type* within <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/crm/contacts|CRM contacts>.

I expected to get back a collection of associated object, in this instance companies, but I am only getting back 1 object although the contact has many. It appear only the primary associated company is being return?

REQUEST
```GET <https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/contacts/801/associations/companies?limit=500&amp;hapikey=>```
RESPONSE
```{
  "results": [
    {
      "id": "5470019826",
      "type": "contact_to_company"
    }
  ]
}```
Is this the expected behaviour?
